cn.crowdos.kernel.constraint

Class DateInterval

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.crowdos.kernel.constraint.DateInterval
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Constraint, Decomposable<Constraint>

    public class DateInterval
extends Object
implements Constraint
    A constraint that represents a date interval between a start date and an end date. The constraint can be decomposed into multiple sub-constraints, each representing a smaller date interval. The constraint can be satisfied by a date condition that falls within the date interval.
